      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a lot stronger. i like the passion. i'm just a little worried about the \"dismantle barriers\" part. some people online seem to think these initiatives actually go against meritocracy and just create more division. how should i handle those kinds of comments if they pop up on the post?",
